import {NavLink, Outlet} from 'react-router-dom';

import Subnavigation from '../layouts/subnavigation'
import SubnavItem from '../layouts/subnavitem'

import JavascriptLogo from '../assets/logo-javascript.svg'

import styled from 'styled-components'
import '../styles/theme.css'

const Services = () => (
  <StyledContainer>
    <Subnavigation title='Services'>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/services/frontend'>Frontend</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>  
      <SubnavItem src={JavascriptLogo}>
        <NavLink to='/services/javascript'>Javascript</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/services/backend'>Backend</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/services/mobile'>Mobile</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem> 
    </Subnavigation>
    <Outlet/>
  </StyledContainer>
);

const StyledContainer = styled('div')`
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 200px auto;
`;

export default Services;
